://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article-live/israeli-war-cabinet-delays-meeting-on-post-war-gaza-syria-accuses-israel-of-strike/0000018c-b396-d45c-a98e-bbde1ec20000</guid></item><item><title>自10月7日以来，英国最大的警察部队宗教仇恨犯罪急剧上升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/britains-largest-police-forces-see-sharp-rise-in-religious-hate-crimes-since-october-7/0000018c-b359-db94-afbd-b37965d10000</link><description>哈马斯-以色列冲突爆发后几周内，英国许多最大的警察部队记录的反犹太仇恨犯罪数量急剧上升</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 02:30:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/britains-largest-police-forces-see-sharp-rise-in-religious-hate-crimes-since-october-7/0000018c-b359-db94-afbd-b37965d10000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列的土壤是由多力多滋组成的，没有稳定性。我 2024 年的计划被取消了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-29/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-soil-is-made-of-doritos-theres-no-stability-my-plans-for-2024-are-canceled/0000018c-b2be-db94-afbd-b2ff2c430000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名活动策划者哀悼特拉维夫一个时代的结束，一名社会工作者解释了她如何从情感要求高的工作中放松下来</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 23:50:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-29/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-soil-is-made-of-doritos-theres-no-stability-my-plans-for-2024-are-canceled/0000018c-b2be-db94-afbd-b2ff2c430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列历史学家摩西·齐默尔曼表示，哈马斯大屠杀表明犹太复国主义已经失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-hamas-pogrom-demonstrates-that-zionism-has-failed-says-historian-moshe-zimmermann/0000018c-b225-d45c-a98e-bb6d24480000</link><description>作为以色列研究德国历史的先驱学者，Moshe Zimmermann 教授回顾了 20 世纪 30 年代的欧洲，以了解以色列的发展方向</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-hamas-pogrom-demonstrates-that-zionism-has-failed-says-historian-moshe-zimmermann/0000018c-b225-d45c-a98e-bb6d24480000</guid></item><item><title>受害者亲属称，被控刺死妻子的以色列人有暴力和虐待历史</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-accused-of-stabbing-wife-to-death-had-history-of-violence-victims-relatives-say/0000018c-b23d-db94-afbd-b27d1ac20000</link><description>亲戚告诉《国土报》，雷切尔·博博特的丈夫涉嫌谋杀，他“嫉妒得发疯”，并告诉她，“她要么和他在一起，要么就埋在地下”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 22:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-accused-of-stabbing-wife-to-death-had-history-of-violence-victims-relatives-say/0000018c-b23d-db94-afbd-b27d1ac20000</guid></item><item><title>调查发现，在另外两人被杀 15 分钟后，以色列国防军开枪射杀了一名以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-shot-one-israeli-hostage-15-minutes-after-two-others-were-killed-probe-finds/0000018c-b24c-d45c-a98e-bb4cf73b0000</link><description>据以色列军方调查，士兵只搜查了关押三名人质的大楼底层。 Samer Fuad El-Talalka、Yotam Haim 和 Alon Shamriz 在二楼呼救。五天后，他们被以色列国防军枪杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 21:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-shot-one-israeli-hostage-15-minutes-after-two-others-were-killed-probe-finds/0000018c-b24c-d45c-a98e-bb4cf73b0000</guid></item><item><title>“美国犹太人不确定哪种威胁最紧迫——来自左翼还是右翼的反犹太主义”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/its-uncertain-which-threat-is-most-pressing-antisemitism-from-the-left-or-the-right/0000018c-b14a-db94-afbd-b17bca2d0000</link><description>记者马修·康蒂内蒂 (Matthew Continetti) 表示，美国犹太人对加沙战争后反犹太主义抬头感到震惊，并警告极右翼公开言论可能会影响像生命之树犹太教堂枪击案凶手这样的“可怕的精神病患者”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 20:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/its-uncertain-which-threat-is-most-pressing-antisemitism-from-the-left-or-the-right/0000018c-b14a-db94-afbd-b17bca2d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列人在耶路撒冷以南的刺伤袭击中受伤，袭击者被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/two-wounded-in-suspected-stabbing-attack-south-of-jerusalem-assailant-shot/0000018c-b1ea-d45c-a98e-bbeeb3070000</link><description>袭击发生后，两名20多岁的受害者被送往医院，袭击者被枪杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 19:51:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/two-wounded-in-suspected-stabbing-attack-south-of-jerusalem-assailant-shot/0000018c-b1ea-d45c-a98e-bbeeb3070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在中部城市罗德刺死幼童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-stabs-toddler-to-death-in-central-city-of-lod/0000018c-b1a1-d014-a3cd-bbbf8e200000</link><description>警方认为嫌疑人患有精神疾病；男孩的母亲说，这名男子不知从哪里突然跳出来，在没有任何挑衅的情况下刺伤了她在婴儿车里的儿子，也没有试图伤害她</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 18:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-stabs-toddler-to-death-in-central-city-of-lod/0000018c-b1a1-d014-a3cd-bbbf8e200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，内塔尼亚胡的司法政变卷土重来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-28/ty-article/.highlight/with-israel-at-war-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-with-a-vengeance/0000018c-b146-d45c-a98e-bb4e59d20000</link><description>最初的司法改革计划可能会被搁置，但政府还有更危险的空间，可以不受限制和不被注意地扩大权力。公众心烦意乱，忙着恐慌或聚集在旗帜周围</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 18:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-28/ty-article/.highlight/with-israel-at-war-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-with-a-vengeance/0000018c-b146-d45c-a98e-bb4e59d20000</guid></item><item><title>不负责任地使用抗菌药物构成健康威胁，而不是加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2023-12-28/ty-article/irresponsible-use-of-antimicrobials-poses-a-health-threat-not-gaza/0000018c-b0f2-d45c-a98e-bbfe6e350000</link><description>对以色列士兵可能在加沙感染耐药疾病并将其传播给以色列普通民众的担忧在很大程度上是没有根据的，特别是考虑到更大的担忧——无论加沙在世界范围内，耐药感染一直在上升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 17:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2023-12-28/ty-article/irresponsible-use-of-antimicrobials-poses-a-health-threat-not-gaza/0000018c-b0f2-d45c-a98e-bbfe6e350000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年是以色列历史上最糟糕的一年——但现在还不是绝望的时候</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-the-worst-year-in-israels-history-but-now-is-not-the-time-to-despair/0000018c-b0cd-db94-afbd-b0fd936d0000</link><description>这一年发生了可怕的事件——弥赛亚政府、司法政变和哈马斯大屠杀——使今年成为“内塔尼亚胡年”。然而，尽管情况很糟糕，以色列仍有时间在 2024 年改变路线</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-the-worst-year-in-israels-history-but-now-is-not-the-time-to-despair/0000018c-b0cd-db94-afbd-b0fd936d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列应该考虑对黎巴嫩进行地面入侵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lebanon-cant-control-hezbollah-israel-must-broaden-military-action/0000018c-af85-db94-afbd-affdcae40000</link><description>真主党与哈马斯一样致力于摧毁以色列和实施 10 月 7 日式的暴行，但更具杀伤力。其不断增加的导弹和无人机袭击以及黎巴嫩的消极态度证明以色列有理由进行广泛的自卫报复</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:40:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lebanon-cant-control-hezbollah-israel-must-broaden-military-action/0000018c-af85-db94-afbd-affdcae40000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔任命新以色列监狱管理局局长，违反战时政府条款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-appoints-new-israel-prison-service-chief-violating-terms-of-wartime-government/0000018c-b0fd-db94-afbd-b0fd39330000</link><description>目前尚不清楚国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔是否有权任命目前担任其安全顾问的科比·雅科比少将，或者是否需要政府做出决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:38:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-appoints-new-israel-prison-service-chief-violating-terms-of-wartime-government/0000018c-b0fd-db94-afbd-b0fd39330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔美国人朱迪·韦恩斯坦·哈盖 (Judi Weinstein Haggai) 于 10 月 7 日被谋杀，据信被哈马斯绑架</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-american-judi-weinstein-haggai-believed-kidnapped-by-hamas-was-murdered-on-oct-7/0000018c-b120-d014-a3cd-bb3ece670000</link><description>10 月 7 日早上，朱迪和她的丈夫加迪在尼尔奥兹基布兹散步时失踪。一周前，家人获悉加迪在袭击当天被谋杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-american-judi-weinstein-haggai-believed-kidnapped-by-hamas-was-murdered-on-oct-7/0000018c-b120-d014-a3cd-bb3ece670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长呼吁各国如果需要加沙难民请发送电子邮件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/israels-fm-calls-on-countries-to-email-if-they-want-gaza-refugees/0000018c-b0de-db94-afbd-b0ff9ec70000</link><description>伊莱·科恩在电视上说：“只需写下该国的地址即可。”他补充说，欢迎接纳叙利亚和乌克兰难民的国家也接纳加沙人</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/israels-fm-calls-on-countries-to-email-if-they-want-gaza-refugees/0000018c-b0de-db94-afbd-b0ff9ec70000</guid></item><item><title>原定周四在美国大屠杀博物馆举行的反以色列抗议活动被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-protest-planned-for-thursday-at-u-s-holocaust-museum-is-canceled/0000018c-b0ec-d45c-a98e-bbec47560000</link><description>在博物馆发表声明后，一个名为“反对种族灭绝医生”的新组织取消了抗议活动，声称“利用大屠杀历史对幸存者和受害者的记忆构成严重冒犯”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-protest-planned-for-thursday-at-u-s-holocaust-museum-is-canceled/0000018c-b0ec-d45c-a98e-bbec47560000</guid></item><item><title>新报告显示，以色列的贫困率是发达国家中最高的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-poverty-rate-is-among-the-highest-in-the-developed-world-new-report-shows/0000018c-b055-d45c-a98e-bb5d02af0000</link><description>国家保险研究所的报告显示，2022 年所有人口部门的贫困都会增加，三分之一的以色列家庭生活在粮食不安全之中——这一比例在以色列阿拉伯社会中最高</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:37:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-poverty-rate-is-among-the-highest-in-the-developed-world-new-report-shows/0000018c-b055-d45c-a98e-bb5d02af0000</guid></item></channel></rss>